* pattern_bt.sno
* Bottleneck: pattern backtracking with alternation.
* Alternation of 4 choices + SPAN in an unanchored search, 500 iters.
    &ANCHOR = 0
    PAT = ('aaa' | 'bbb' | 'ccc' | 'ddd') SPAN('abcd') . W
    S = 'xxxxxxxxxxbbbccccddddaaaaxxxxxxxxxxbbbccccddddaaaa'
    N = 0
LOOP    S PAT                           :F(DONE)
    N = LT(N, 500) N + 1                :S(LOOP)
DONE    OUTPUT = N
END
